      "skill1": "■ Activates when attacking with Full Charge and self is in Maillard status. Affects all allies.\nMaillard Duration ▲ 2.5 sec.\n■ Activates when attacking with Full Charge and self is in Blanching status. Affects all allies.\nBlanching Duration ▲ 2.5 sec.\n■ Activates after landing 3 normal attack(s) without Full Charge. Affects all allies.\nMaillard: ATK ▲ 10% of the skill user's ATK for 10 sec.\nRemoves Blanching.\n■ Activates after maintaining 3 Full Charge status for more than 1 sec. Affects all allies.\nBlanching: ATK ▲ 10% of the skill user's ATK for 10 sec.\nRemoves Maillard.",
